<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><lyrics>[V1]
 1- tḥt ạlṣlyb bạrkʿ ʿndk .. wạtạ̉ml fy jrạḥạtk
 wạ̉nạ bạjy lk bjrwḥy .. wʿạrf ạ̹n sẖfạỷy fyk
 ḥty̱ wlw kạn ạlrạ̉s sqym .. ḥty̱ wlw kạn ạlkl mryḍ
 ạ̉nạ bạjy lk bjrwḥy . wʿạrf ạ̹n sẖfạỷy fyk
 ạlqrạr- (bjldtk sẖfyt) 4
 2- kl ạ̹sạʾẗ lm tgẖtfr .. wjrḥ fy ạlqlb ạ̹tḥfr
 ḥty̱ lw kạn bqạlh snyn .. ạ̹ymạny fyk ạ̹nt yạ mʿyn
 3- bạ̉rfʿ ạlmjd lạsmk .. fy ṣlybk qwẗ sẖfạʾ
 qwẗ tḥryr qwẗ tbryr .. qwẗ frḥ wslạm wʿzạʾ</lyrics>
